The specimen data for nearly all of the zeomorph taxa and their outgroups are given in Tyler et al (2003) (except see Tyler et al 1989 for the two acanthuroids and Tyler 1968, 1980 and Santini & Tyler 2003 for the two tetraodontiforms). Materials examined that are not already listed in Tyler et al (2003) are arranged in this publication, listing museum number, number of specimens in each lot, and standard length (SL). Museum abbreviations follow Leviton et al (1985). The two fossil tetraodontiforms are listed and described in Tyler & Sorbini (1996) and Santini & Tyler (2003). The remaining specimens are given in this publication.
